OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774649478
OL,3,CWhat Iranians think about Trump's
OL,4,Cpeace plan
OL,6,FWritten by ITV News Producer Zahra
OL,7,FManji
OL,9,FAmid the heavy strikes and sirens,
OL,10,Fworry hangs over the people of Iran
OL,11,Fabout their country's future.
OL,13,FIran and the United States are at an
OL,14,Fimpasse, with each side hardening its
OL,15,Fposition over peace talks.
OL,17,FThousands more US troops are nearing
OL,18,Fthe region, while Tehran has tightened
OL,19,Fits grip on the crucial shipping
OL,20,Froute, the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
