OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774649478
OL,3,CWhat Iranians think about Trump's
OL,4,Cpeace plan
OL,6,FAs the war approaches the one-month
OL,7,Fmark, US officials continue to insist
OL,8,Fan end to hostilities is close and
OL,9,Fproposed a 15-point ceasefire deal,
OL,10,Fwhich Iran has rejected.
OL,12,FThe US proposal is said to include
OL,13,Fsanctions relief, a rollback of Iran's
OL,14,Fnuclear program, limits on missiles,
OL,15,Fand the reopening of the Strait of
OL,16,FHormuz, through which a fifth of the
OL,17,Fworld's oil is normally shipped.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
