OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774649478
OL,3,CWhat Iranians think about Trump's
OL,4,Cpeace plan
OL,6,FIran issued its own plan via state TV,
OL,7,Fwhich includes a halt to killings of
OL,8,Fits officials, means to make sure no
OL,9,Fother war is waged against it,
OL,10,Freparations for the war, the end of
OL,11,Fhostilities, and Iran's sovereignty
OL,12,Fover the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,14,F"No negotiations have happened with
OL,15,Fthe enemy until now, and we do not
OL,16,Fplan on any negotiations," Iran's
OL,17,Fforeign minister later said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
