OL,3,CWhat Iranians think about Trump's
OL,4,Cpeace plan
OL,6,FWithout offering a specific threat,
OL,7,FPresident Trump said on Truth Social
OL,8,Fon Thursday that Iranian leaders
OL,9,Fshould engage "before it is too late,
OL,10,Fbecause once that happens, there is NO
OL,11,FTURNING BACK".
OL,13,FAs these talks continue, the death
OL,14,Ftoll in Iran is mounting, with the US-
OL,15,Fbased Human Rights Activists News
OL,16,FAgency (HRANA) recording more than
OL,17,F1,400 civilian deaths, 15% of them
OL,18,Fchildren.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
