OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774649478
OL,3,CWhat Iranians think about Trump's
OL,4,Cpeace plan
OL,6,FITV News asked four people living in
OL,7,FIran how they feel about Trump's
OL,8,Fproposed peace plan.
OL,10,FNames have been changed for the
OL,11,Fpurpose of anonymity.
OL,13,FMahtab, 42, stay-at-home mum from
OL,14,FTehran
OL,16,F"If the war is stopped and the regime
OL,17,Fstays in power, I think for many of us
OL,18,FIranians, it would feel like a kind
OL,19,Fof... collective death.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774649478
OL,3,CWhat Iranians think about Trump's
OL,4,Cpeace plan
OL,6,F"In my opinion, this is a betrayal of
OL,7,Fthe people of Iran, and a trampling
OL,8,Fover the blood of all those young
OL,9,Fpeople who went (out) and gave their
OL,10,Flives and everything they had".
OL,12,FArmin, 40, from Shiraz, works in IT
OL,14,F"That you have this shadow of fear and
OL,15,Fthreat hanging over you, no matter
OL,16,Fwhere you are in the city. Armed,
OL,17,Fmasked people who set up checkpoints
OL,18,Fand try to randomly stop and question
OL,19,Fpeople.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774649478
OL,3,CWhat Iranians think about Trump's
OL,4,Cpeace plan
OL,6,F"The fear that if this war doesn't
OL,7,Flead to (regime change) or the war
OL,8,Fends and they remain, then in reality
OL,9,Fwe are living in a country that is
OL,10,Flike a big prison, controlled by a
OL,11,Fgroup of armed thugs who will gain
OL,12,Fcomplete control over everything and
OL,13,Fthe situation will become much more
OL,14,Fpainful than what we are currently
OL,15,Ffacing."
OL,17,FSomayeh, 33, upper-middle-class, from
OL,18,FKeraj
OL,26,@oD@IpmoD@Wpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774649478
OL,3,CWhat Iranians think about Trump's
OL,4,Cpeace plan
OL,6,F"The fear that has settled in all of
OL,7,Four hearts is that the war might end
OL,8,Fand Trump might want to negotiate with
OL,9,FIran and that he might even talk to
OL,10,Fthe key figures who are still there
OL,11,Fand haven't been removed, and bring
OL,12,Fthem back into power and that really
OL,13,Fis not in the interest of us, the
OL,14,Fpeople of Iran.
OL,16,F"We wanted the war for the sake of
OL,17,Fchanging the government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
